channel.title: [HELP] Connecting To Null Server On Port Null [ERROR]
channel.description:
Hey guys, I am as you may have guessed am trying to make a webclient. The only thing is it loads just fine until you get to the login screen. When I log in it says connecting to null server on port null. Then Error connecting to server. It never did that to me before. What's Going On?
Please Help If you can. I appreciate all the help I can get.
Thanks! :D Ghostly150
